      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "•  Forked from Kieran's Pinchflat (commit 67d8bd5)\n•  Added a few features and bug fixes\n•  Going forward: \n•    Critical bug fixes & security patches only\n•    No additional new features, no DB schema changes\n•  Stays 100% upstream-compatible\n\n✔  Migrate BACK to Kieran's Pinchflat\n     anytime — nothing is locked in",
      "originalText": "•  Forked from Kieran's Pinchflat (commit 67d8bd5)\n•  Added a few features and bug fixes\n•  Going forward: \n•    Critical bug fixes & security patches only\n•    No additional new features, no DB schema changes\n•  Stays 100% upstream-compatible\n\n✔  Migrate BACK to Kieran's Pinchflat\n     anytime — nothing is locked in",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "index": "aT"
