      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "•  Forks from this fork's Pinchflat 1.4.0\n•  Active development — new features & UX\n•  Freedom to evolve the database schema\n•  Aimed to be community-driven, more maintainers\n\n✖  One-way migration (Pinchflat → Tubeless)\n     no supported path back to upstream",
      "originalText": "•  Forks from this fork's Pinchflat 1.4.0\n•  Active development — new features & UX\n•  Freedom to evolve the database schema\n•  Aimed to be community-driven, more maintainers\n\n✖  One-way migration (Pinchflat → Tubeless)\n     no supported path back to upstream",
